title: What Not to Wear
resume: What Not to Wear was an American makeover reality television show based on a British show of the same name. The program premiered in 2003 and aired on TLC in the United States and Canada. It also aired on Discovery Travel & Living Europe, on People+Arts in Spain as ¡No te lo pongas!, and in Portugal and Brazil as Esquadrão da Moda. Foreign versions of show air in Mexico, Colombia, Argentina and Italy. What Not to Wear was hosted by Stacy London and Clinton Kelly. On March 6, 2013, TLC announced that the tenth season of What Not to Wear would be the last.
